## Agent final message

> Completed! `query80.preql` has been written and validated with `trilogy run query80.preql`. The query:
> 
> - Uses `raw.all_sales` (multi-channel consolidated fact)
> - Filters for date range 2000-08-23 through 2000-09-22
> - Filters item.current_price > 50 and promotion.channel_tv = 'N'
> - Filters channel_dim_id is not null (outlet recorded)
> - Computes channel label ('store channel', 'catalog channel', 'web channel')
> - Computes outlet identifier as the prefixed business code
> - Aggregates total_sales (sum of ext_sales_price), total_returns (coalesced sum of return_amount), and total_profit (sum net_profit - sum coalesced return_net_loss)
> - Uses `by rollup channel_label, outlet_identifier` for per-outlet, per-channel subtotals, and grand total
> - Orders by channel_label and outlet_identifier nulls first, limit 100
> 
> The output runs cleanly — 100 rows with grand total, per-channel subtotals, and per-outlet detail rows.

